;[[Minbar]] (منبر) : a raised pulpit in the mosque where the Imam stands to deliver sermons
;Minhaj (منهج) : methodology, e.g. methods, rules, system, procedures. 
;[[Miqat]] (ميقات ) : intended place
;[[Isra and Miraj|Miraj]] (المعراج) : the Ascension to the Seven Heavens during the Night Journey ''See also: [[isra]]''
;[[Muezzin|Mu'adhdhin]] (مأذن): a person who performs the call to prayer
;[[Mu'awwidhatayn|{{transl|sem|Mu‘awwidhatayn}}]] (المعوذتين) : suras [[Al-Falaq]] and [[an-Nas]], the "Surahs of refuge", should be said to relieve suffering (also protect from Black Magic)
