;[[Muta'sibūn]] : fanatics
; [[Mutaween]]  (مطوعين) Singular = mutawa: Religious police. 
;[[Mutawatir|Mutawātir]] (متواتر)  :  "agreed upon"--used to describe hadith that were narrated by many witnesses through different narration chains (isnads) leading back to Muhammad

== N ==
